title: Huge Shop! House with Apartment 160 Victory Lane, Crescent
text:
Huge Shop! House with Apartment 160 Victory Lane, Crescent ad date: 10/21/2015 
House with Apartment 160 Victory Lane, Crescent City, CA Situated on 3.66 private acres is this spacious well cared for home plus 1 bedroom apartment w 3/4 bath, living room & kitchen. The BIG BONUS is a fisherman's dream: a 40'x 60'. 2400 sq. ft. shop w/3 corner lofts & forklift, 14' doors for RV stg. Large upstairs master suite has balcony that overlooks this gorgeous property. Bath has Jacuzzi & walk-in shower, dual sinks. Kitchen bonus is adjacent dinette w/access to back deck. Custom oak cabinetry. Separate formal dining and large great room with wood stove. No. 1500511 $349,000
